title: Box office: 'Singh Is Bliing' is second biggest opener of 2015
text: In true Khiladi style, Akshay Kumar has wrapped up his year at the box office on a high note. After delivering three back-to-back hits — 'Baby', 'Gabbar Is Back' and 'Brothers', in that order — the actor has only raised the bar with his latest release, 'Singh Is Bliing' for a couple of reasons.
